BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313355734@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260306T023728Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260306T091500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260306T101500
SUMMARY:Eagle Rock Reservation
DESCRIPTION:Let's Walk!!\nJOIN US FOR A WALK. WE WALK AT A MODERATE PACE O
 N UNPAVED PATHS.\n\nWe will hike for about an hour - 3.5 miles. We will be
  walking on trails in the woods\, so appropriate footwear\, long pants & s
 ocks\, and bug spray.\n\nWill will meet at:\n[https://goo.gl/maps/7rRRTiXC
 ntdE1neD7](https://goo.gl/maps/7rRRTiXCntdE1neD7) Eagle Rock Trail Parking
  Lot by Kiosk#1\n\nIf you enter from Eagle Rock Way\, go pass the Highlawn
  and stay left. There will be a parking lot at the end of the curve to you
 r right.\n\nEagle Rock Reservation is 408 acres of hills\, streams\, and v
 alleys located on the borders of West Orange\, Verona\, and Montclair\, Ne
 w Jersey. Though located in the middle of the most densely populated count
 y in the most densely populated state in the country\, the Reservation is 
 mostly undeveloped and boasts an extensive trail system within its borders
 .\n\n**Please make sure to RSVP and arrive 5 minutes prior to start time.*
 *\n\nFOLLOW US ON INSTAGRAM - letswalkmeetup\n\nDisclaimer: If you join us
  for a hike\, please understand that you are responsible for your own prep
 aredness and well-being and will hold no one else liable in case of injury
  or mishap. Event will be canceled in the event of extreme weather.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lets-walkprogram/events/313355734/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260214T150133Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260214T150133Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313641043@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260306T023728Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260306T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260306T110000
SUMMARY: Let's Walk!! Orange Reservoir Loop
DESCRIPTION:Let's Walk!!\n**DUE TO TRAIL CONDITIONS AT EAGLE ROCK THE EVEN
 T FOR FRIDAY HAS BEEN MOVED TO ORANGE RESERVOIR**\n\n**WE START ON TIME SO
  PLEASE ARRIVE 5 MINUTES EARLY.**\n\nJoin us for a walk at the Orange Rese
 rvoir Loop located near Turtle Back Zoo.\n\nThe loop is a 1.8-mile paved t
 rail around the reservoir. This is a very popular area for birding\, runni
 ng\, and walking. The walk is for all skill levels.\n\nYou can park at McL
 oone's Boathouse and we will meet in the lot at the trail entrance. Please
  dress for the weather\, wear appropriate shoes\, bring water\, and a frie
 ndly disposition.\n\nRain or extreme weather will cancel the event.\n\nDis
 claimer: If you join us for a hike\, please understand that you are respon
 sible for your own preparedness and well-being and will hold no one else l
 iable in case of injury or mishap.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lets-walkprogram/events/313641043/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260305T002715Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260305T002715Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313605205@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260306T023728Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260307T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260307T113000
SUMMARY:Verona Park
DESCRIPTION:Let's Walk!!\nJOIN US FOR A WALK\n\nWe will meet at the benche
 s in front of the boathouse.\n\nWe will walk the loop around the park. The
  goal will be at least three miles\, but there is plenty of opportunity to
  stop or continue to fit your personal goals.\n\nWe will be walking on a p
 aved surface.\n\nWe walk at a medium speed.\n\nPlease plan to arrive 5 min
 utes **early** so that we can **start on time.**\n\nVerona Park is 54.32 a
 cres with a lake running through it. It is bordered by Lakeside and Bloomf
 ield Avenues in the southern part of Verona. It is the fifth largest park 
 in the Essex County system\, making it a great place to walk.\n\nDisclaime
 r: If you join us for a hike\, please understand that you are responsible 
 for your own preparedness and well-being and will hold no one else liable 
 in case of injury or mishap. Event will be canceled in the event of extrem
 e weather.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lets-walkprogram/events/313605205/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260302T180319Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T180319Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
